{
  "stem": "13469.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, like everybody else, we were all collected up in a square, the top of the road, top of our road there, and then we're put in trucks that were taken to a nearby station, [INAUDIBLE] railway station.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There, we were put on the train of cattle trucks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in the trucks, we were taken to this camp, Westerbork-- [INAUDIBLE] Westerbork as it's called-- which was a transit camp.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What do you remember of the journey in the truck from Amsterdam to Westerbork?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The first bit was in a truck, and then in the cattle trucks kind of thing, yeah.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nothing, really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I suppose [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was not a big journey.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Probably take a couple of hours, something like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think it was a lot of waiting around and all that because the [INAUDIBLE] started, as I said, very early in the morning.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was probably late in the evening by the time we got to Westerbork and sorted out and everything else.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we spent all day hanging around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But it was all fairly orderly and methodical kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I didn't really see too much in the way of beating or shouting or any of that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Everybody just did as they were told.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Everybody knew about it because we'd seen, heard, about these roundups before.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we realized that eventually it probably would be our turn.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't really remember any of the names.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just father, mother, Eve, [INAUDIBLE] and me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there would be other people there that we knew, but we just can't remember [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I've found lots of letters and lots of names of people, but I can't really recall them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I can't remember them in any kind of way.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
